        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Hire Student Veterans Act</strong></p> <p>This bill expands the work opportunity tax credit to allows employers a credit for hiring veterans who are receiving educational assistance under programs provided by the Department of Defense or the Department of Veterans Affairs.</p>]]>
        </text>
